{"TopicId":197935,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Space Program 2 to be released in 2022 [Discussion Thread]","CreatedByName":"Arco123","CreatedById":201477,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-05T17:18:00Z","PageNum":50,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:29:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224132956\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652720856\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes you were, but you were right for the same reason why a broken clock is right twice a day. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ENo, I\u0027m right, because April 2023 is the corporate deadline for KSP 2. The publisher can promise the players anything, but it\u0027s better not to deceive the shareholders.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IncompetentSpacer","CreatedById":205214,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:32:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224132999\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652724027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137773\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Catto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, Catto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe steam community is a wasteland of toxic people. I expected them to throw tantrums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not too saddened, as preorders will possibly come in around November/December, In time for Christmas, so more people can get the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich means i don\u0027t have to save all my money!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis. And it does not only apply to this game\u0027s steam forum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-----------\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould I like it to come out earlier - sure...\u00A0 But I haven\u0027t paid anything for it yet so I couldn\u0027t care less. Now, if they had opened for preordering, taken the money and then communicated postponement of the game , the case would be different (typical for 50% of early release games on steam).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:34:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224133021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652725751\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ENo, I\u0027m right, because April 2023 is the corporate deadline for KSP 2. The publisher can promise the players anything, but it\u0027s better not to deceive the shareholders.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat has nothing to do with your previous post unless you are implying games can only come out at the very end of a fiscal year for some reason?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MARL_Mk1","CreatedById":192535,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:34:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMe, externally reacting to the announcement \u003Cem\u003E\u0022It\u0027s fine guys, good luck! This game is gonna be a banger!\u0022\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso me\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022cover1.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022450\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/031/671/cover1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xjames","CreatedById":185156,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:44:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni feel like pacman. the only thing I say is\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nmac mac mac mac mac mac mac\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nmac?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:49:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224133025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652726045\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat has nothing to do with your previous post unless you are implying games can only come out at the very end of a fiscal year for some reason?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EJudging by the news on the game, or rather their absence, development is being delayed a lot.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESo far, no blogger has been invited to play the alpha version, there is no real gameplay with sending a small rocket even beyond the atmosphere.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAnd they promised us a lot!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETherefore, I am sure that the game will be delayed until the last deadline. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAlso see here:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.07\u0022 height=\u0022626\u0022 width=\u0022977\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T18:53:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224133031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652726968\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EJudging by the news on the game, or rather their absence, development is being delayed a lot.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESo far, no blogger has been invited to play the alpha version, there is no real gameplay with sending a small rocket even beyond the atmosphere.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAnd they promised us a lot!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETherefore, I am sure that the game will be delayed until the last deadline. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAlso see here:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.07\u0022 height=\u0022626\u0022 width=\u0022977\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for clarifying. So like I said, a clock.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"t_v","CreatedById":213541,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T19:05:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224133031\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197935\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652726968\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAlso see here:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002264.07\u0022 height=\u0022626\u0022 width=\u0022977\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DE9b1XL.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you just take an image of someone in the middle of a blink to make a point? Who does that!? I have personally only seen that in the absolute worst of political arguments, and I was not expecting you to debase yourself like that. In case it was not the blink: beards are fine facial hair for someone and making a point off of what someone chooses to do with their appearance is equally lowly, yes the background is different and there isn\u2019t a big ol\u2019 smile because this isn\u2019t a reveal, it is a delay that Nate is probably not happy to announce off of the teleprompter. Criticizing people is not a good way to work through whatever is going on around this announcement.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-16T19:18:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the \u003Cspan\u003Elatest \u003C/span\u003Einformation having been just made available, this thread is no longer needed, so we\u0027ll lock this now. Please see here for the latest news on the release window:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022205123\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5816620336\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/208209-release-date-update-from-the-ksp2-team/\u0026amp;do=em